{
  "id": "adv_event_2205_01_02",
  "title": "今のままじゃ\nダメ",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2205_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2205_01_02-ski001.m4a",
      "text": "それじゃあ、今日から改めてよろしくね、千紗",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Well then‚ let's start fresh from today‚ Chisa.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 0.8,
      "endTime": 4.651700592,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2205_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2205_01_02-chs001.m4a",
      "text": "う、うん。こちらこそ……よろしく、お姉ちゃん",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Y-Yeah. I'm looking forward with it… ‚ Onee-chan.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 4.8666666667,
      "endTime": 10.0333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2205_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2205_01_02-ski002.m4a",
      "text": "大会に向けて練習スケジュールを組んだの\nいつもと勝手が違うから、あくまで仮だけどね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I've made a practice schedule for the tournament.\nSince it's different from our usual routine‚ it's just a temporary plan.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 10.2333333333,
      "endTime": 18.6853289923,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_paper-01.m4a",
          "delay": 0
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2205_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2205_01_02-chs002.m4a",
      "text": "わ……お姉ちゃん、さすが……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Wow… Onee-chan‚ you're amazing…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 18.9666666667,
      "endTime": 22.3333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2205_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2205_01_02-ski003.m4a",
      "text": "千紗も意見があればどんどん言って\nいつでも調整するから",
      "translations": {
        "en": "If you have any opinions‚ Chisa‚ feel free to speak up.\nWe can always make adjustments.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 22.7,
      "endTime": 27.3333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2205_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2205_01_02-chs003.m4a",
      "text": "う、うん、分かった……！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Y-Yeah‚ got it…!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 27.5333333333,
      "endTime": 30.1666666666,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2205_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2205_01_02-ski004.m4a",
      "text": "1、2、3、4！\n千紗、大丈夫？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "1‚ 2‚ 3‚ 4!\nChisa‚ are you okay?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 35.2666666667,
      "endTime": 40.8766666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2205_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2205_01_02-chs004.m4a",
      "text": "うん……大丈夫、だよ……っ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yeah… I'm fine…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 41.0666666667,
      "endTime": 46.2666667621,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2205_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2205_01_02-ski007.m4a",
      "text": "（次のステップは……私が一歩引いたら）\n（千紗が目立てるかな）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "(Next step… If I take a step back…)\n(Will Chisa stand out?)",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 46.4666666667,
      "endTime": 51.7738253275,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2205_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2205_01_02-chs007.m4a",
      "text": "（ここで……私が一歩引けば）\n（お姉ちゃんが引き立つかも……）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "(If I take a step back here…)\n(Onee-chan might shine…)",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 52,
      "endTime": 57.5832110086,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "一同",
      "speakerNameEn": "Everyone",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2205_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2205_01_02-chs006.m4a",
      "text": "（せーの……）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "(Ready‚ set…)",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 57.9,
      "endTime": 59.6666666666,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "一同",
      "speakerNameEn": "Everyone",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "……あっ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…Ah!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 60,
      "endTime": 61.2333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2205_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2205_01_02-ski008.m4a",
      "text": "ご、ごめんね？　二人とも下がっちゃったね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "S-Sorry? We both stepped back‚ huh?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 61.4666666667,
      "endTime": 66.0168932915,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2205_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2205_01_02-chs008.m4a",
      "text": "あはは、そうだね……私こそ、ごめんね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ahaha‚ yeah… I'm sorry too.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 66.2333333333,
      "endTime": 70.85859397249999,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2205_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2205_01_02-chs009.m4a",
      "text": "（あ、あれ……？　また二人とも譲っちゃった……）\n（これじゃ、二人とも目立たなくなっちゃう）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "(Huh…? We both yielded again…)\n(We might end up not standing out at all…)",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 73.2333333333,
      "endTime": 81.8546666464,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2205_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2205_01_02-ski009.m4a",
      "text": "千紗、ちょっと休憩にしましょう？\n話し合いもしたいし",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Chisa‚ let's take a break‚ okay?\nI also want to have a discussion.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 82.3,
      "endTime": 88.1333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2205_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2205_01_02-chs010.m4a",
      "text": "そ、そうだね……私も、話したかった",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Y-Yeah‚ that sounds good… I wanted to talk too.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 88.2666666667,
      "endTime": 92.46666666670001,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2205_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2205_01_02-ski010.m4a",
      "text": "なんだかうまくいかないわね……\nグループで練習してる時と感覚が違うというか",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Things don't seem to go well…\nThe feeling is different from when we practice as a group.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 94.4478729248,
      "endTime": 101.7478729248,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2205_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2205_01_02-chs011.m4a",
      "text": "う、うん……お姉ちゃんとなら\n最初からうまく出来ると思ったんだけど……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Y-Yeah… I thought we could do well\nfrom the beginning if it's with Onee-chan…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 102.0145395915,
      "endTime": 108.78724460519999,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2205_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2205_01_02-ski011.m4a",
      "text": "サニピと月ストで練習している時と\n何が違うのかしら……？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "When we practice with Sunny Peace and Moon Tempest…\nWhat's different‚ I wonder…?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 109.0478729248,
      "endTime": 114.0152291757,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2205_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2205_01_02-chs012.m4a",
      "text": "違い、かぁ……うーん……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "The difference‚ huh… Hmm…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 114.2145395915,
      "endTime": 118.8691652934,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2205_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2205_01_02-ski012.m4a",
      "text": "五人グループの時と、二人組ユニットの時……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "In a five-person group‚ and in a duo team…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 119.0812062581,
      "endTime": 123.4407756169,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2205_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2205_01_02-chs013.m4a",
      "text": "……そういえば、サニピでは……いつも怜ちゃんが\nどんどん引っ張ってくれてる……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…Now that you mention it‚ in Sunny Peace…\nRei-chan always takes the lead…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 123.6478729248,
      "endTime": 130.06785149319998,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2205_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2205_01_02-ski013.m4a",
      "text": "確かにそうね。それで言うと……月ストでは\n琴乃ちゃんが怜ちゃんみたいに引っ張ってくれてるかな",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That's true. Speaking of Moon Tempest…\nKotono-chan leads like Rei-chan‚ I guess.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 130.2812062581,
      "endTime": 138.0145395915,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2205_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2205_01_02-ski014.m4a",
      "text": "琴乃ちゃんがはっきり言うタイプだから\n私はバランスをとることが多いかも",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Kotono-chan is straightforward‚ so…\nI tend to balance things out more.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 138.2145395915,
      "endTime": 143.87740786790002,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2205_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2205_01_02-chs014.m4a",
      "text": "怜ちゃんもはっきり言うけど……お姉ちゃんみたいな\n役割の人は、さくらちゃんとか、遙子さんかも",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Rei-chan is straightforward too… But for roles like Onee-chan's…\nSakura-chan and Haruko-san might be for that…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 144.0812062581,
      "endTime": 152.08422206240002,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2205_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2205_01_02-chs015.m4a",
      "text": "私と雫ちゃんは、怜ちゃんが厳しいと\nぷるぷるしてることが多いかな",
      "translations": {
        "en": "When it comes to me and Shizuku-chan‚\nwe often end up trembling when Rei-chan is strict.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 152.2812062581,
      "endTime": 158.3812062581,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2205_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2205_01_02-ski015.m4a",
      "text": "琴乃ちゃんも怜ちゃんも\n自分が厳し過ぎるかもって気にしてたわね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Both Kotono-chan and Rei-chan were\nworried if they were being too strict.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 158.5812062581,
      "endTime": 163.6478729247,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2205_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2205_01_02-ski016.m4a",
      "text": "でも、そっか……普段は私も千紗も\n誰かを引っ張る役割じゃない……か",
      "translations": {
        "en": "But I see… Normally‚ neither me nor Chisa…\nPlay the role of leading someone… right?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 163.9812062581,
      "endTime": 171.6167843819,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2205_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2205_01_02-chs016.m4a",
      "text": "確かに……だから、ちょっとうまくいかないのかも？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That's true… So‚ maybe that's why it's not going well?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 171.9145395915,
